text: Colobothea caramaschii is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Monné in 2005. It is known from Venezuela.BioLib.cz - Colobothea caramaschii. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Colobotheini Category:Beetles described in 2005
